{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"corking-vermicidal-unicorn","description":"## Why\nThe live Jira/LLM tier runs only on `workflow_dispatch`\n(`.github/workflows/external-integration.yml:17-18`), sets `REBAR_RUN_EXTERNAL=1` and\n`ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`/`OPENAI_API_KEY` but maps **no `JIRA_*` secrets** — the Jira credentials\nappear only as a docstring example in `tests/external/test_link_sync_roundtrip_live.py`.\nConsequently API/SDK drift can merge through normal CI with no real integration signal.\nVALIDATED.\n\n## What\nAdd a scheduled, non-destructive canary and wire the missing Jira secrets.\n\n## Scope\n- CI workflow + `tests/external` skip/report plumbing. Non-destructive: read-only or\n  uniquely-tagged fixtures that clean up.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] A scheduled workflow runs the live tier against a dedicated project/account.\n- [ ] The job **fails** if every external test skipped (no silent green on all-skip).\n- [ ] `JIRA_URL`/`JIRA_USER`/`JIRA_API_TOKEN` are wired as workflow secrets (not comments).\n- [ ] The run publishes executed-vs-skipped live-test counts.","id":"5f39-cb52-9355-492f","parent_id":"bf50-2131-271b-4fdc","priority":2,"tags":["p1","ci","integration"],"ticket_type":"story","title":"Scheduled external contract canary that fails when all live tests skip"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783784819441794001,"uuid":"6cf0c9f3-537e-4c16-8754-44d5c75ad313"}